http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/Sankranti-Sobha-in-Srikakulam-from-January-11/article13989903.ece

Srikakulam district administration is making elaborate arrangements for Sankranti Sobha which will be celebrated from January 11 to 13 in Srikakulam, according to District Collector P. Lakshmi Narasimham.Various cultural events will be organised as part of the celebrations in the NTR Municipal Stadium. Labour Minister K.Atchannaidu will formally inaugurate the programme. The government hoped that the event would help youngsters to know the importance of festivals, culture and traditions of Indians.